</blockquote>
<h2>Finding #5: AI Overviews Have Changed What "Ranking" Even Means &#123;#finding-5&#125;</h2>
<p><strong>AI Overviews now appear on roughly 48% of searches. 93% of AI Mode searches end without a click.</strong></p>
<p>This finding changes everything about the "does AI content rank?" question. In 2026, "ranking" is no longer just about Position #1 on Google's blue links. It is about being cited in AI-generated answers across Google AI Overviews, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini.</p>
